-- Microsoft CEO Says Canal+ Can Offer Content on Xbox Game Console
-- B y   M a t t h e w   C a m p b e l l
-- 2010-10-07T14:39:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/microsoft-ceo-says-canal-can-offer-content-on-xbox-game-console.html
Microsoft Corp. signed an accord
which will allow French pay-tv company Canal Plus to offer
content on its Xbox game console, Chief Executive Officer Steve
Ballmer said in Paris today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
